               <p>OLD COURT. MONDAY, OCTOBER 22.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Sergeant Arabin.</p>
               <p>2344. 
               
                  <persName id="t18321018-138-defend1292" type="defendantName">
                     GEORGE 
                     BALDRY
                  <interp inst="t18321018-138-defend1292" type="surname" value="BALDRY"></interp>
